description: Faster One was developed from a sans serif italics. In order to create an impression of velocity, the horizontal and gradual lines generate the idea of the image of the wind. Ideal for writing headlines where efficiency and speed are priorities. To contribute to the project contact Eduardo Tunni. Updated September 2015: Internal metadata corrected.
